sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant OP as Operator
    participant CLI as deepview memory acquire remote
    participant G as Authorization Gate
    participant P as SSHDDProvider
    participant SSH as paramiko.SSHClient
    participant H as Remote Host (sudo dd)
    participant EB as EventBus

    OP->>CLI: --transport ssh --host target --confirm<br/>--authorization-statement "..."

    CLI->>G: check --confirm + auth statement
    alt missing
        G-->>CLI: AuthorizationError
        CLI-->>OP: abort
    end

    Note over CLI: 5s warning banner + countdown

    CLI->>P: build_remote_provider("ssh", endpoint, ctx)
    P->>EB: publish RemoteAcquisitionStartedEvent
    P->>SSH: connect(host, identity_file, known_hosts)
    SSH-->>P: authenticated channel

    P->>H: exec "sudo dd if=/dev/mem bs=1M"
    loop for each chunk
        H-->>P: raw bytes
        P->>P: write chunk to output file
        P->>EB: publish RemoteAcquisitionProgressEvent<br/>(bytes_done, bytes_total, stage="stream")
    end

    P->>EB: publish RemoteAcquisitionCompletedEvent
    P-->>CLI: AcquisitionResult(path, size, elapsed)
    CLI-->>OP: success
